  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>This is the Brainrot Sahur RPG.</strong><br><strong>Compact top-down action game with classless abilities and gear.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Fight,  grind, make your build, perform deadly combos and still be done in time for work.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167100/extras/fdf6d32e7ecf6aae534faca3661bee31.poster.avif?t=1751377424\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167100/extras/fdf6d32e7ecf6aae534faca3661bee31.webm?t=1751377424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167100/extras/fdf6d32e7ecf6aae534faca3661bee31.mp4?t=1751377424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Code: Blue combines action from beat-em-up games with arpg itemization and abilities. Carefully select your rares and epics to create satisfying combos and survive the onslaught of enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167100/extras/b1c19d27dc837a2fc8c0c08f3c68921f.poster.avif?t=1751377424\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167100/extras/b1c19d27dc837a2fc8c0c08f3c68921f.webm?t=1751377424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167100/extras/b1c19d27dc837a2fc8c0c08f3c68921f.mp4?t=1751377424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Itemization matters! Will your gear give you enough armor or will you be slashed-and-diced like a cutlet of raw beef? Damage types matter! Slash Damage from swords is weak versus well-armored opponents, use Blunt Damage weapons like the Gauntlets or Big Hammer instead! Will you survive long enough to escape or will you succumb to defeat by dodging at the wrong moments!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167100/extras/e13662817bb29882fde139aa3d920545.poster.avif?t=1751377424\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167100/extras/e13662817bb29882fde139aa3d920545.webm?t=1751377424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167100/extras/e13662817bb29882fde139aa3d920545.mp4?t=1751377424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Music by Karl Casey @ White Bat Audio and Android128, Icons from , Brainrot models edited from: alex.cgwarrior</p>",
